  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Claymore.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category:</strong> Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Claymore Clan, Level 4+</p><p>You can peer far past the vision of a normal Claymore, granting you newfound scouting abilities. You gain the following benefits:</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Wisdom or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>You gain an additional use of your Silver-Eyes clan feature, and your base chakra sight range is increased to 120 feet. You also gain darkvision out to the same range.</p></li><li><p>You may choose another non-humanoid creature type to count as Unnatural Beings for you.</p></li><li><p>As an action, you can choose to focus on a single creature's energy up to 10 miles away as you enter a trance-like state by taking the Search Skill Action on a creature whose name you know or are aware of. If you focus on a creature's energy this way, you can see a direct path to them and see them as if you were 30 feet away.</p></li></ul>",
